==圣日==
{{main|巴哈伊圣日}}
在巴哈伊历中有十一个圣日，而其中的九天应停止工作休息。<ref name="nsausa">{{cite web|title=The Badi Calendar |url=http://www.bahai.us/system/files/BahaiCalendarOptimized.pdf |accessdate=2006-09-23 |publisher=bahai.us |author=National Spiritual Assembly of the United States |date=2006-03-05 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060928212618/http://www.bahai.us/system/files/BahaiCalendarOptimized.pdf |archivedate=2006-09-28 }}</ref>[[里兹万节|里兹万节]]，一个十二天的节日，[[巴哈欧拉|巴哈欧拉]]宣示他的神圣使命的纪念日，是巴哈伊的至圣之日，被称为“至大节日”<ref name="ridvan">{{cite web | title = Ridvan | first = John | last = Walbridge | url = http://bahai-library.com/walbridge_encyclopedia_ridvan | date = 2003-10-02 | accessdate = 2006-09-23 | archive-date = 2011-05-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110514050105/http://bahai-library.com/walbridge_encyclopedia_ridvan | dead-url = no }}</ref>

伊斯兰的阴历中，[[巴孛|巴孛]]和[[巴哈欧拉|巴哈欧拉]]的出生日是连续的两天：分别是[[穆哈兰月|穆哈兰月]]的第一天和第二天<ref name="rob4">{{cite book |author= Taherzadeh, Adib |authorlink= Adib Taherzadeh |year= 1987 |title= The Revelation of Bahá'u'lláh, Volume 4: Mazra'ih & Bahji 1877-92 |publisher= George Ronald |location= Oxford, UK |isbn= 0853982708 |pages= 334 |url= http://www.peyman.info/cl/Baha%27i/Others/ROB/V4/p329-350Ch22.html |access-date= 2010-09-14 |archive-date= 2018-09-16 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20180916224645/http://www.peyman.info/cl/Baha'i/Others/ROB/V4/p329-350Ch22.html |dead-url= no }}</ref> 世界正义院决定依照太阳历来庆祝这两天，但是主管部门或个人有权力将其更改为依照阴历庆祝，这通常会使其移动十一或十二天。

